{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/object-oriented-programming/use-dot-notation-to-access-the-properties-of-an-object","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"object-oriented-programming","demoType":null,"title":"Koristi tačke pisanja da dobiješ atribute objekta","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Poslednji izazov stvorio je nešto sa različitim karakteristikama. Sada ćete videti kako da dobijete vrednosti tih karakteristika. Evo primera:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let duck = {\n  name: \"Aflac\",\n  numLegs: 2\n};\nconsole.log(duck.name);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Notacija sa tačkom se koristi za ime objekta, <code>duck</code>, praćeno imenom svojstva, <code>name</code>, da bi se dobila vrednost <code>Aflac</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d7dac367417b2b2512b74","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Ispišite oba svojstva objekta <code>dog</code> u vašoj konzoli.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301333,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/object-oriented-programming/use-dot-notation-to-access-the-properties-of-an-object"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"let dog = {\n  name: \"Spot\",\n  numLegs: 4\n};\n// Only change code below this line","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vaš kod bi trebalo da koristi <code>console.log</code> za štampanje vrednosti svojstva <code>name</code> objekta <code>dog</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(/console.log\\(.*dog\\.name.*\\)/g.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj kod treba da koristi <code>console.log</code> za štampanje vrednosti svojstva <code>numLegs</code> objekta <code>dog</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(/console.log\\(.*dog\\.numLegs.*\\)/g.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#object-oriented-programming","dashedName":"use-dot-notation-to-access-the-properties-of-an-object","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"object-oriented-programming","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/object-oriented-programming/create-a-method-on-an-object","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/object-oriented-programming/create-a-basic-javascript-object","id":"587d7dac367417b2b2512b74","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"const funModule = (function () {\n  return {\n    isCuteMixin: obj => {\n      obj.isCute = () => true;\n    },\n    singMixin: obj => {\n      obj.sing = () => console.log(\"Singing to an awesome tune\");\n    }\n  };\n})();","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/object-oriented-programming/use-dot-notation-to-access-the-properties-of-an-object"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}